data.description: FABULOUS TOWNHOME IN THE VERANDAHS IN SE WINTER HAVEN! This beautifully maintained one-story two bedroom, two bath is a fantastic open floorplan with soaring 15-foot vaulted ceilings. In addition, a bonus/ flex room, with pocket doors, is a great place for a home office or to keep an eye on the kids while you are in the kitchen. You can enjoy a cook’s kitchen with plenty of wood cabinets and counter space complete with a breakfast bar with solid surface counters! Upgraded wood plank luxury vinyl in the main living area, bedrooms and flex space. The updated lighting and a neutral color palette will make it easy to decorate. The 19-foot high entry and multiple transom windows welcomes natural light to this carefree lifestyle! Enjoy the large walk in closet and luxurious main bath with an oversized walk-in shower. Convenient inside laundry. Attached single car garage with a paver driveway. Plenty of room for guest parking and you can enjoy the community pool and the fishing pier at Reeves Lake with your family and friends! HOA includes basic cable, internet, and provides maintenance of exterior, lawn, irrigation and community pool.  This home has a water softener system and is on city water and city sewer. Roof 2018, A/C 2023. Convenient location with excellent schools, restaurants and shopping. Just minutes from Winter Haven’s Legoland and less than an hour to Disney World! The only thing this home is missing is you! Make an appointment today for your private showing.
